<subSubSection type="description">
<paragraph pageNumber="15">[[ worker ]]. Monomorphes. Epinotum releve en bosse. Metanotum notablement saillant sur le profil du corselet. Afrique. Ocelles peu apparents.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection type="nomenclature">
<paragraph pageNumber="15">
Type: 
<taxonomicName LSID-HNS="urn:lsid:biosci.ohio-state.edu:osuc_concepts:34166" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Plagiolepis" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Plagiolepis decora Santschi" lsidName-HNS="Plagiolepis decora Santschi" order="Hymenoptera" pageNumber="15" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="decora">Plagiolepis decora Santschi</taxonomicName>
